title: Golden Age of Video Games - Age of the Cartridge v1.6
description:
This is the Age of the Cartridge collection v1.6, which includes all the cartridge-based games from the Golden Age of Video Games.

What is the Golden Age of Video Games?

Well, I spent over ten years researching and playing full game collections (over 10,000 games) of previous generations of video game systems to create a collection that I feel represents the "golden age of video games". With this collection, posterity may now play a nearly comprehensive collection of the best classic games (even the translated and obscure ones) without tons of research or sorting through full ROM collections that are 90% crud. This collection includes the Golden Age collection of the Game Boy, GBC, GBA, NES, SMS, MSX, SNES, Sega Genesis, Sega 32X, Neo Geo, and N64 systems!
